        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Used by every command unless overridden in the modal. Five built-in styles are listed; the modal lets you search 10,000+ citation styles.",
          "target": "除非在模态框中覆盖，否则每个命令都使用此设置。列出了五种内置样式；模态框允许您搜索 10,000 多种引文样式。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Plain text is the safest default. HTML preserves italics and inline markup but only applies to styles selected via the modal — the five built-in styles emit text only and fall back automatically.",
          "target": "纯文本是最安全的默认选项。HTML 保留斜体和内联标记，但仅适用于通过模态框选择的样式——五种内置样式仅输出文本并自动回退。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Whether the command swaps the identifier in place or appends the citation after it.",
          "target": "命令是就地替换标识符还是在其后附加引文。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Sends ?provenance=1 with each citation request. Adds the upstream registry (Crossref / PubMed / DataCite / etc.), fetch timestamp, and transform version to each item so you can see where the metadata came from.",
          "target": "每次引文请求都发送 ?provenance=1。将上游注册中心（Crossref / PubMed / DataCite 等）、获取时间戳和转换版本添加到每个项目，以便您查看元数据的来源。"
        },
